CO2 Sensor (SGP30)	I2C (0x5A)	LuftqualitÃ¤t (eCO2 + TVOC)

PiTop 2 - Pausenzone
Komponente	Port	Funktion
Step Counter (BMA400)	I2C (0x14)	Schritte, Kalorien, Distanz

ğŸ“Š Datenbank-Schema

Sessions Tabelle
- session_id (UUID)
- user_name (TEXT)
- device_id (TEXT)
- start_time (TIMESTAMP)
- end_time (TIMESTAMP)
- total_work_time (INTEGER) -- in Sekunden
- total_break_time (INTEGER) -- in Sekunden
- pause_count (INTEGER)
- timer_status (TEXT) -- 'idle', 'working', 'break', 'work_ready', 'ended'

CO2 Measurements Tabelle
- session_id (UUID, FK)
- co2_level (INTEGER) -- ppm
- tvoc_level (INTEGER) -- ppb
- is_alarm (BOOLEAN)
- alarm_type (TEXT) -- 'warning', 'critical', NULL
- created_at (TIMESTAMP)

Break Data Tabelle
- session_id (UUID, FK)
- pause_number (INTEGER)
- step_count (INTEGER)
- calories_burned (INTEGER)
- distance_meters (INTEGER)
- device_id (TEXT)
